Screening for Lung Cancer With Low-Dose Computed Tomography: Updated Evidence 
Report and Systematic Review for the US Preventive Services Task Force.

Jonas DE(1)(2), Reuland DS(3)(4)(5), Reddy SM(1)(6), Nagle M(7), Clark SD(8), 
Weber RP(1)(4), Enyioha C(9), Malo TL(5), Brenner AT(5), Armstrong C(1)(4), 
Coker-Schwimmer M(1)(4), Middleton JC(1)(4), Voisin C(1)(4), Harris RP(3)(4).

