Routine versus selective intraoperative cholangiography during cholecystectomy: 
systematic review, meta-analysis and health economic model analysis of 
iatrogenic bile duct injury.

Rystedt JML(1), Wiss J(2), Adolfsson J(2), Enochsson L(3)(4), Hallerbäck B(5), 
